keyPolicies.policyDescription: Encourage enterprise and back small business, keeping jobs taxes low and cutting red tape; Invest in infrastructure to attract businesses and good jobs across the whole of the UK; Reward work, help people into a job and lower the benefit cap; Create 3 million new apprenticeships so young people get the skills to succeed.
